These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: fishing, camping
Job: videographer, designer
1. Job:videographer is in an even position##4
2. Job:designer == Hobby:camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | camping | fishing |
| Job     | designer    | videographer   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, hot-chocolate
Sport: badminton, surfing
1. Sport:badminton is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda        |
| Sport      | badminton  | surfing |

 #################################
 
